data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!! Improvements Completed on NE Heights Gem! New Landscaping, Interior & Exterior Paint, and Wood Flooring! This cozy 3 bed/2 bath home is the perfect. Spacious bedrooms and two living areas, including a family room for entertaining. Wood fireplace for roasting marshmallows and warming-up from the cold winter days. Great Neighborhood with FANTASTIC neighbors! Excellent location close to schools, parks, shopping, and foothill trails!!! Beautiful Mountain Views!
